Treat everyone with respect. Absolutely no harassment, witch hunting, sexism, racism, homophobia, transphobia or hate speech of any kind will be tolerated in this server.Please keep in mind your server profiles and pictures too!
No NSFW or obscene content. Including text, images, or links featuring nudity, sex, hard violence, or other graphically disturbing content.
Controversial topics such as religion or politics are not allowed. Please be cautious introducing sensitive topics such as gender, race, sexuality etc... Don't post content which references illegal activity or restricted substances.
No self-promotion (server invites, advertisements, fundraisers etc.) without permission from a staff member. This includes DMing fellow members. Please do not request that other members DM you.
Do not buy/sell/trade/give away/beg or request that of others members.
